    "completed_on": null,
    "comments_count": 16,
    "assignees": "Chris Traynor, Emerald Green, Justyna Acosta",
    "app_url": "https://3.basecamp.com/4226914/buckets/45555854/todos/9702854157",
    "description": "<div>The clients are requesting a new referral landing page for Action Garage Doors, modeled after the referral page used by Utah Garage Door. Since this is the client's first experience with this type of page, we will need to create the content from scratch. The page should clearly explain the referral program and highlight the client’s maximum reward of <strong>up to $500</strong>.<br><br>\n</div><div><strong><br>Requested Outcome</strong></div><ul>\n<li>Create a brand-new referral landing page on the Action Garage Doors website at with this URL -&gt;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://actiongaragedoor.net/referral\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://actiongaragedoor.net/referral</a>\n</li>\n<li>The page should be fully created from scratch, since the client confirmed there is no existing content for this page.</li>\n</ul><div><strong>Reference</strong></div><ul>\n<li>Use this page as the design/content inspiration: <a href=\"https://utahgaragedoors.net/referral-program/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://utahgaragedoors.net/referral-program/</a>\n</li>\n<li>The client wants their page to closely resemble the Utah garage doors landing page, while reflecting Action Garage Doors’ own payout structure and messaging.</li>\n</ul><div><br></div><div><strong>Required Page Elements</strong></div><ul>\n<li>New referral landing page created with the slug [ /referral ]</li>\n<li>QR code provided for the page</li>\n<li>Messaging should reflect that users can <strong>earn up to $500</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Include the referral payout tier information provided by the client</li>\n<li>Overall page structure and presentation should closely resemble Utah Garage Doors.<br><br>\n</li>\n</ul><div><strong><br>Referral Payout Tiers to Include</strong></div><ul>\n<li>$0–$99 → $5</li>\n<li>$100–$499 → $10</li>\n<li>$500–$999 → $25</li>\n<li>$1,000–$2,499 → $50</li>\n<li>$2,500–$4,999 → $100</li>\n<li>$5,000–$9,999 → $150</li>\n<li>$10,000–$14,999 → $250</li>\n<li>$15,000+ → $500</li>\n</ul><div><br></div><div><strong>Assets</strong></div><ul><li>Client mentioned a QR code is attached and must be included on the page<br><br>\n</li></ul><div><strong>Notes for PM / Team</strong></div><ul>\n<li>This is a net-new landing page, not an edit to an existing page</li>\n<li>Requested slug is /referral</li>\n<li>Creative/content direction should be based on the&nbsp; Utah Garage Doors example page, but adjusted for Action Garage Doors branding and payout tiers</li>\n<li>Ensure payout language reflects the client’s exact tier structure and “earn up to $500” messaging</li>\n</ul><div><bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiLmdpZDovL2JjMy9BdHRhY2htZW50LzgyNzk5NjIwNj9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiCHB1cgY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVA==--8ccbe06a87fefdec7a6b646ff4a7ab541eb7e85c\" content-type=\"image/png\" url=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bee76ef0-2488-11f1-960b-0242ac120004/previews/full\" href=\"https://storage.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bee76ef0-2488-11f1-960b-0242ac120004/download/QRCode.png\" filename=\"QRCode.png\" filesize=\"6812\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" previewable=\"true\" presentation=\"gallery\"><figure>\n    <img srcset=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bee76ef0-2488-11f1-960b-0242ac120004/previews/full?dppx=2 2x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bee76ef0-2488-11f1-960b-0242ac120004/previews/full?dppx=1 1x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bee76ef0-2488-11f1-960b-0242ac120004/previews/full?dppx=3 3x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bee76ef0-2488-11f1-960b-0242ac120004/previews/full?dppx=4 4x\" src=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bee76ef0-2488-11f1-960b-0242ac120004/previews/full\">\n  <figcaption>\n    QRCode.png\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment></div><div></div>",
