    "description": "<div>Seeking help with the following client requests please.&nbsp;<br><br>I am adding the ticket verbatim to be sure. Please do let us know too if we have further queries or possible concerns, we can coordinate with their AM.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</div><div>Client has requested to add ip4:149.72.155.154 to their SPF record in DNS in Go Daddy.<br>Are we willing to give Microtech delegate access to their domain? If so, could you send it to <a href=\"mailto:helpdesk@microtechboise.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">helpdesk@microtechboise.com</a>? They are their MSP and may need to add/update DNS records from time to time.</div><div><br></div><div>1. SPF Record Update</div><ul>\n<li>Add the following IP to the existing SPF record: ip4:149.72.155.154</li>\n<li>Ensure:<ul>\n<li>Existing SPF entries remain intact</li>\n<li>No duplication or overwrite of current SPF configuration</li>\n<li>Final SPF record remains valid and properly formatted</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul><div>\n<br>2. Domain Access Request (GoDaddy)</div><ul>\n<li>Evaluate request to provide delegate access to Microtech (MSP)</li>\n<li>If approved:</li>\n<li>Grant appropriate level of access to: <a href=\"mailto:helpdesk@microtechboise.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">helpdesk@microtechboise.com</a>\n</li>\n<li>Ensure:<ul>\n<li>Access level is appropriate (not excessive)</li>\n<li>Does not compromise account security</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul><div><br></div><div>Dependencies / Approvals Required</div><ul>\n<li>Confirm:</li>\n<li>Clixsy has access to the GoDaddy account</li>\n<li>Approval from client (Marissa or primary contact) to:</li>\n<li>Modify SPF record</li>\n<li>Grant third-party domain access</li>\n</ul><div>&nbsp;<bc-attachment content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.horizontal-rule.html\"><figure>\n  <hr>\n</figure></bc-attachment><br>Thanks much! <br><br>cc <bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vNDkxOTE1ODI_ZXhwaXJlc19